search_results.title: Tyson Yunkaporta
search_results.snippet: Tyson Yunkaporta is an academic, arts critic, researcher, and member of the Apalech Clan in far north Queensland. He is the author of Sand Talk.

search_results.title: Tyson Yunkaporta
search_results.snippet: Tyson Yunkaporta is an Australian academic, author, and indigenous thinker. He is a member of the Apalech Clan from Far North Queensland.

search_results.title: Dr. Tyson Yunkaporta - Cornell CALS
search_results.snippet: Tyson Yunkaporta is an Aboriginal scholar, founder of the Indigenous Knowledge Systems Lab at Deakin University in Melbourne, and author of Sand Talk.
